    "body": "@ellisonbg your comment about the flashing is true in the too big \"medium\" screenshot above, but I still think there is a happy medium that is less objective and more based on tenants of human interaction design. One concern is that there are many users of IPython that are not developers like you and I who will just get by with a suboptimal experience and never know to look into modifying the .css. I mean maybe they'd get motivated enough to google it and stumble across a stackoverflow question about how customize IPython :)\n"
